    archive: 'icon-archive',

    edit: 'icon-edit',

    file: 'icon-file',
    clone: 'icon-clone',

    tag: 'icon-tag',

    downArrow: 'icon-down-arrow',

    tiStamp: 'ti-stamp',
    tiPencilAlt: 'ti-pencil-alt'
};
export const ICO = {
    write: 'ico-write',
    files: 'ico-files',
    user: 'ico-user',
    bag: 'ico-bag',
    package: 'ico-package',
    bookmark: 'ico-bookmark-alt',
    wallet: 'ico-wallet',
    briefcase: 'ico-briefcase'
};
